    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Formerly the game was named Enhanced: Vengeance</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auctus unfolds centuries in the future, on a distant planet in a far-off solar system. Humanity has mastered space travel and established new colonies across the stars. Medical and technological advancements have made cybernetic limbs and enhancements not only possible, but practical and easy to install by specialists. This is where your story begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to find the people who tortured you, maimed you and left you for dead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/8066a6d8ec44f61e07cf65d9f4200e32.poster.avif?t=1772289784\" width=594 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/8066a6d8ec44f61e07cf65d9f4200e32.webm?t=1772289784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/8066a6d8ec44f61e07cf65d9f4200e32.mp4?t=1772289784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choices have consequences</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate a world of morally complex characters, each driven by their own goals, secrets, and sins. Will you manipulate them, stand by them, or simply shoot them? Your choices will forge the path ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/7cff581abeb93e5246f5d17375d8823c.poster.avif?t=1772289784\" width=594 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/7cff581abeb93e5246f5d17375d8823c.webm?t=1772289784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/7cff581abeb93e5246f5d17375d8823c.mp4?t=1772289784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Integrated weapons and abilities into your cybernetics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Install devastating weapons and cutting-edge abilities directly into your cybernetics. Launch rockets, unleash gouts of flame, or discharge arcs of lightning straight from your palms. Fly with jets built into your legs, blink across the battlefield in a flash, or spot lootable items with enhanced vision. In this world, your body isn’t just augmented - it is a weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/8c0719b355b59e47d32890dbe84fd0c1.poster.avif?t=1772289784\" width=594 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/8c0719b355b59e47d32890dbe84fd0c1.webm?t=1772289784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288420/extras/8c0719b355b59e47d32890dbe84fd0c1.mp4?t=1772289784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friendly and hostile factions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character statistics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory and equipment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vendors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random and tiered loot drops</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialog</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save the state of the game at any time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied locations to explore</p></li></ul>",
